name: CATastrophic sense 🔮
description: #Part2 Bê was a little worried of what would be the next adventure of Rupi and Zel, so he made an appointment with this very mysterious taologuer to see what the future was holding for him. But then he saw that little cat face on the crystal ball, AARGH what is that?? I can only say that this was a CATastrophic experience and that Bê is not even a little bit happy with what he saw on that crystal ball… Can you humans guess what will be Rupi and Zel's next step? Stay tuned for their next adventure! A big meow to you all. 🐾🔮 P.S.: this was a collab with @eternagnose who made this incredible soundtrack!
